  "title": "supervisor",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Work closely with operations, sales and kitchen team to ensure the clients’ needs are met</p></li><li><p>Oversee and monitor all operations and logistics for all catering events</p></li><li><p>Manage manpower planning to suit different catering needs</p></li><li><p>Monitor service, food and beverage standards and resolve any issues if necessary</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain good working relationship with clients and handle customer complaints</p></li><li><p>Monitor and maintain vehicle standard, food quality, service standard & smooth running of the catering office and central kitchen</p></li><li><p>Understanding with and complying with the mandatory hygiene standards and requirements</p></li></ul>",
